			<Text>We must protect the reputation of our Artists. Pay off whoever you need to.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_FAKE_PAINTING_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Oh well. Isn't all Art a lie?</Text>
		</Row>
